"title": "4966: present, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4966: present, the",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's blessings are available now and are to be received in faith and contentment. It is dangerous to live only for current blessings and pleasures.</p>\n<h2>Blessings promised for the present</h2>\n<h3>The blessing of God's presence now</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:13\">HAG 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:6\">DEU 31:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:57\">1KI 8:57</a></p>\n<h3>The blessing of Jesus Christ's presence now</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:23\">MAT 1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:14\">ISA 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:8\">ISA 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:10\">ISA 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:20\">MAT 18:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:20\">MAT 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:18\">JHN 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:10\">ACT 18:10</a></p>\n<h3>The blessing of the Spirit's presence now</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:25-John14:27\">JHN 14:25–14:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7\">JHN 16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13-John16:16\">JHN 16:13–16:16</a></p>\n<h3>Other blessings given in the present</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:25\">EXO 23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:13\">1KI 3:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr1:12\">2CH 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:3-Ps121:8\">PSA 121:3–121:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:8\">1TI 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:9\">1PE 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>Future blessings are partially fulfilled in the present</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:23\">ROM 8:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:30\">ROM 8:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:5\">2CO 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3\">EPH 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22-Heb12:24\">HEB 12:22–12:24</a></p>\n<h2>Prayer for present provision and blessing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:3\">LUK 11:3</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:11\">MAT 6:11</a> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:20\">GEN 28:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov30:8\">PRO 30:8</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:4\">LUK 11:4</a> <em>prayers for spiritual provision</em></p>\n<h2>The secret of contentment in the present</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:10-Phil4:13\">PHP 4:10–4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:6-1Tim6:8\">1TI 6:6–6:8</a></p>\n<h2>The dangers of living for the present</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:12-Eccl3:13\">ECC 3:12–3:13</a></strong> <em>Ecclesiastes in particular reflects upon the emptiness of life without God. Though the good things of the present life are a gift from God and to be valued as such, they cannot bring ultimate fulfilment</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:15-Luke12:20\">LUK 12:15–12:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:24\">ECC 2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:18\">ECC 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:15\">ECC 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:7\">ECC 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:9\">ECC 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:13\">ISA 22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:32\">1CO 15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:19\">PHP 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9-1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:9–6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:17\">JAS 4:13–4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></p>\n<h2>The challenge of the present</h2>\n<h3>The challenge to respond to God now</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:39-Deut4:40\">DEU 4:39–4:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:1\">DEU 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:11\">DEU 7:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:13\">DEU 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:15-Deut30:16\">DEU 30:15–30:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:7-Ps95:8\">PSA 95:7–95:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:6\">ISA 55:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:12\">HOS 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7\">HEB 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>The challenge to serve God now</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:15-Eph5:16\">EPH 5:15–5:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:5\">COL 4:5</a></p>",
